{"tid":1385003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港台爆料 - 揭元朗721警不查白衣人","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T23:44:20.000Z","uid":89349,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6c4341e81e487658d0fe79b40bf1d0d5f348f2","tid":1385003,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Hg2P91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Hg2P91.png&h=5f9bc40c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"899c32248b3f316529c415e6981b539edaa29985","tid":1385003,"uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"【港台公開閉路電視片段　揭元朗721警不查白衣人】<br />\n<br />\n元朗7月21日晚發生大批白衣暴徒，肆意襲擊途人的暴行，香港電台節目獲得當晚片段，發現警察巡邏車多次巡經白衣人，卻沒有下車截查。<br />\n<br />\n港台《鏗鏘集》取得當晚多個閉路電視片段，指警察巡邏車至少3次巡經有大批白衣人聚集的鳳攸北街，但無警員下車截查。先是晚上9時半，有一架警察巡邏車經過，當時鳳攸北街上正有大批白衣人聚集，警方無理會；而由晚上9時半至10時半期間，至少3次有警車經過鳳攸北街，期間不見警員落車。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-30-2019/54720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-30-2019%2F54720&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=9acedcd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-30-2019/54720</a><br />\n#香港電台 #閉路電視 #白衣人 #警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=6a0bcdd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=48c07cdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=f1f38198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=8dcb1265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\n<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"https://apple.co/2IfgPoP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2IfgPoP&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=b47eabc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2IfgPoP</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HqB4Q4&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=f8f41392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"27f14effc50ded3f19b7bbcafc9ef4101baf7910","tid":1385003,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc6c4341e81e487658d0fe79b40bf1d0d5f348f2","tid":1385003,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Hg2P91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Hg2P91.png&h=5f9bc40c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:53:07.000Z","msg":"死黑警"},{"pid":"dc5467822f07a3afc572e652e645b54f999d07cc","tid":1385003,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma